          %h2
            Planning & Refining the Idea
          %p
            As KiwiJar is an app that hasn’t been done before, it involved extensive planning to make sure we were including all neccesary features for Phase 1 but not overloading it and taking away from the core message.
          %h4
            The main goals were to:
          %ul
            %li
              %span
                Outline and refine the user experience
            %li
              %span
                Decide upon and eliminate as neccesary the key features for Phase 1
            %li
              %span
                Design a clear and intuative user interface
            %li
              %span
                Produce a future proof style guide (or pattern library) that can be used to develop the project over time

